      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $f : {\\R} \\to {\\R^+}$ une fonction de classe $\\mathcal{C}^2$.\nOn suppose : $\\forall\\ x \\in \\R,\\ |f''(x)| \\le M$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f : {\\R} \\to {\\R^+}\\)</span> une\nfonction de classe <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{C}^2\\)</span>.\nOn suppose : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\forall\\ x \\in \\R,\\\n|f&#39;&#39;(x)| \\le M\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "de201d79-915b-4c03-9987-453deb66ca1c",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que : $\\forall\\ x,y \\in \\R,\\ f(x) + yf'(x) + \\frac {y^2}2M \\ge 0$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\forall\\ x,y \\in \\R,\\ f(x)\n+ yf&#39;(x) + \\frac {y^2}2M \\ge 0\\)</span>.</p>\n"
